Package: oroboros
Title: High-Resolution Respirometry Data Processing and Analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Bente", "Theeuwes", , "bente.theeuwes@oroboros.at", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Streamlines the workflow for high-resolution respirometry by 
    providing tools to import DatLab 8 files in bulk. The package automates 
    the extraction of flux data by set marks. It performs standardized 
    calculations, such as flux per volume, specific flux, flux control ratio,
    and baseline correction. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.5)
LazyData: true
Imports:
	mongolite (>= 4.0.0),
	jsonlite (>= 2.0.0)

